  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="accesibility-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[++++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Action and Expression: Internalize Executive Functions. Check for understanding by inviting students to rephrase game directions in their own words. Be sure unused counters are removed from the area so there is no confusion when counting counters after the “spill.”</p>
